{
  "stem": "7337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To give you an example, my father's business was called English Club before World War I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they smashed his stores, because they thought it was-- they were English-owned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he changed the name to Deutsche Hut-Vertrieb.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the Nazis came in, they smashed the shops, because they were called Deutsche, and he was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he changed it for the second time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he changed it to Der Hut-Vertrieb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which means 'the hat distributor.' And it meant he could retain the logo of the organization.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he couldn't do right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] anything that was called German could not be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wouldn't allow that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Nazis wouldn't allow it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they started burning books.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They started boycotting Jewish shops-- before Hitler became chancellor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that when he did become chancellor, things didn't really change.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The pace merely accelerated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They suffered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the Jews, the Jewish businesses suffered, definitely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the earlier part of Hitler's reign, the time that I was in Germany, it was nothing compared to probably from 1937, '38 onwards, when he really-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when he had published his final solution, which was to eliminate the Jews totally-- Jews, gypsies, homosexuals, and cripples.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Those were all to be eliminated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's when he-- what I would-- the concentration camps, at first, were labor camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they became concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And finally, they became death camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in fact, Chelmno was the first camp in Poland, where gas was used.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but we learned it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we were no longer in Germany then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was saw little of it, because I was in a camp from April '33 until June '33.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
